These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
There are 4 different nationalities: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the french is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. the french is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the french is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

