.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, indian, russian
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the russian##1
2. the australian is the fan of punk##1
3. the indian is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

