.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, pilot, project-manager, teacher
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the pilot##3
2. the teacher is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the teacher##3
4. the teacher is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the coach is between the teacher and the pilot##2
6. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the fish is between the coach and the owner of the goat##2
8. the coach is on the left or right of the pilot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | pilot | coach      | teacher | project-manager |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

