.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, mouse, turtle
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hamster and the person eating pepper##2
4. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pepper is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| Pet    | turtle     | hamster | cat     | mouse  |

