.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, electronic, jazz
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the fan of jazz is between the fan of disco and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

