.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, tea, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta   | water   | juice      | tea      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | water-polo | biathlon |

