.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's hobby is chess##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving | chess         | board-games   | magic-tricks |
| Sport   | soccer    | skateboarding | weightlifting | ice-hockey   |

