.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, reading, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | board-games | reading    | woodworking |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

