.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, software-developer
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the manager is in an even position##4
2. the manager is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the entrepreneur and the person driving the helicopter##2
4. the manager is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the software-developer##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | pilot   | software-developer | manager |
| Transport   | van          | jet-ski | helicopter         | subway  |

